### Ghana District Assembly — Revenue Unit
### Digital Taxation & Revenue Tracking System
### REST Client test file — compatible with VS Code REST Client extension
### Usage: Install "REST Client" extension, then click "Send Request" above any request.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@contentType = application/json

### ─── VARIABLES (populated after login) ──────────────────────────────────────
# After running "Admin Login", copy access/refresh tokens into these variables:
@accessToken = PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
@refreshToken = PASTE_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE
@taxAdminToken = PASTE_TAX_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

###
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# AUTH MODULE
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### [AUTH-01] SYS_ADMIN Login — Success
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "sysadmin@demo.gov.gh",
  "password": "DemoPass123!"
}

###

### [AUTH-02] TAX_ADMIN Login — Success
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "taxadmin1@demo.gov.gh",
  "password": "DemoPass123!"
}

###

### [AUTH-03] Login — Wrong Password (expects 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "sysadmin@demo.gov.gh",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

###

### [AUTH-04] Login — Unknown Email (expects 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "nobody@example.com",
  "password": "DemoPass123!"
}

###

### [AUTH-05] Refresh Access Token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "refresh": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

###

### [AUTH-06] Get Current Admin (Me)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [AUTH-07] Protected Route — No Token (expects 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/me

###


###
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# ADMIN USER MANAGEMENT (SYS_ADMIN only)
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### [ADMIN-01] List All Admins (SYS_ADMIN)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [ADMIN-02] Create New Admin (SYS_ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "email": "newadmin@demo.gov.gh",
  "password": "DemoPass123!",
  "name": "New Admin",
  "role": "TAX_ADMIN"
}

###

### [ADMIN-03] Create Admin — TAX_ADMIN Forbidden (expects 403)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{taxAdminToken}}

{
  "email": "hacker@demo.gov.gh",
  "password": "DemoPass123!",
  "name": "Not Allowed",
  "role": "TAX_ADMIN"
}

###

### [ADMIN-04] Update Admin Role (SYS_ADMIN)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/PASTE_ADMIN_ID_HERE
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "role": "TAX_ADMIN"
}

###
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# TRADER REGISTRATION (Public — no auth)
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### [REG-01] Register Trader — Web Channel (expects 201)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Akua Mensah",
  "phone_number": "+233241234567",
  "business_type": "food_vendor",
  "location": {
    "region": "Greater Accra",
    "district": "Accra Central",
    "market_name": "Makola Market"
  }
}

###

### [REG-02] Register Same Phone Again — Idempotent (expects 200 + same TIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Akua Mensah",
  "phone_number": "+233241234567",
  "business_type": "food_vendor",
  "location": {
    "region": "Greater Accra",
    "district": "Accra Central",
    "market_name": "Makola Market"
  }
}

###

### [REG-03] Register — Invalid Phone Format (expects 400/422)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Test Trader",
  "phone_number": "not-a-phone",
  "business_type": "retail",
  "location": {
    "region": "Ashanti",
    "district": "Kumasi",
    "market_name": "Central Market"
  }
}

###

### [REG-04] Register — Missing Required Fields (expects 400/422)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "No Phone Trader",
  "business_type": "retail"
}

###

### [REG-05] Register with 0-prefixed phone (Ghana format)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Kofi Asante",
  "phone_number": "0271234567",
  "business_type": "clothing",
  "location": {
    "region": "Ashanti",
    "district": "Kumasi Central",
    "market_name": "Asafo Market"
  }
}

###


