# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# TIN LOOKUP (Public — no auth)
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### [TIN-01] TIN Lookup — Found
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/tin/lookup
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "phone_number": "+233241234567"
}

###

### [TIN-02] TIN Lookup — Not Found (expects 404)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/tin/lookup
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "phone_number": "+233299999999"
}

###

### [TIN-03] TIN Lookup — Invalid Phone Format (expects 400/422)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/tin/lookup
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "phone_number": "12345"
}

