# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# USSD SIMULATION (Africa's Talking webhook format)
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# NOTE: Use a unique sessionId for each independent flow test.
#       text field uses * as delimiter for previous inputs.

### [USSD-01] Initial Menu
POST {{baseUrl}}/ussd/callback
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

sessionId=test_sess_001&serviceCode=*714%23&phoneNumber=%2B233281234567&text=

###

### [USSD-02] Select "1" — Register Business
POST {{baseUrl}}/ussd/callback
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

sessionId=test_sess_001&serviceCode=*714%23&phoneNumber=%2B233281234567&text=1

###

### [USSD-03] Enter Name
POST {{baseUrl}}/ussd/callback
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

sessionId=test_sess_001&serviceCode=*714%23&phoneNumber=%2B233281234567&text=1*Yaw+Boateng

###

### [USSD-04] Select Business Type (1 = Food Vendor)
POST {{baseUrl}}/ussd/callback
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

sessionId=test_sess_001&serviceCode=*714%23&phoneNumber=%2B233281234567&text=1*Yaw+Boateng*1

###

### [USSD-05] Select Region (2 = Ashanti)
POST {{baseUrl}}/ussd/callback
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

sessionId=test_sess_001&serviceCode=*714%23&phoneNumber=%2B233281234567&text=1*Yaw+Boateng*1*2

###

### [USSD-06] Enter Market Name
POST {{baseUrl}}/ussd/callback
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

sessionId=test_sess_001&serviceCode=*714%23&phoneNumber=%2B233281234567&text=1*Yaw+Boateng*1*2*Kumasi+Central+Market

###

### [USSD-07] Confirm Registration (1 = Yes) — Creates trader, returns TIN
POST {{baseUrl}}/ussd/callback
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

sessionId=test_sess_001&serviceCode=*714%23&phoneNumber=%2B233281234567&text=1*Yaw+Boateng*1*2*Kumasi+Central+Market*1

###

### [USSD-08] Check TIN (option 2 from main menu)
POST {{baseUrl}}/ussd/callback
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

sessionId=test_sess_002&serviceCode=*714%23&phoneNumber=%2B233281234567&text=2

###

### [USSD-09] Check TIN — Use own number ("0")
POST {{baseUrl}}/ussd/callback
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

sessionId=test_sess_002&serviceCode=*714%23&phoneNumber=%2B233281234567&text=2*0

###

### [USSD-10] Help (option 3)
POST {{baseUrl}}/ussd/callback
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

sessionId=test_sess_003&serviceCode=*714%23&phoneNumber=%2B233291234567&text=3

###

### [USSD-11] Invalid Main Menu Option
POST {{baseUrl}}/ussd/callback
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

sessionId=test_sess_004&serviceCode=*714%23&phoneNumber=%2B233291234568&text=9

###


