# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# TRADERS LIST & DETAIL (TAX_ADMIN+ required)
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### [TRADERS-01] List Traders — All (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/traders?page=1&page_size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [TRADERS-02] List Traders — Filter by Channel: web
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/traders?channel=web&page=1&page_size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [TRADERS-03] List Traders — Filter by Channel: ussd
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/traders?channel=ussd&page=1&page_size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [TRADERS-04] List Traders — Filter by Business Type
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/traders?business_type=food_vendor&page=1&page_size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [TRADERS-05] List Traders — Filter by Region
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/traders?region=Greater+Accra&page=1&page_size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [TRADERS-06] List Traders — Full Text Search
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/traders?search=Kofi&page=1&page_size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [TRADERS-07] List Traders — Date Range Filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/traders?date_from=2026-01-01&date_to=2026-03-31&page=1&page_size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [TRADERS-08] List Traders — Combined Filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/traders?channel=web&region=Ashanti&business_type=clothing&page=1&page_size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [TRADERS-09] Trader Detail — Valid ID (replace with real ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/traders/PASTE_TRADER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [TRADERS-10] Trader Detail — Not Found (expects 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/traders/000000000000000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [TRADERS-11] List Traders — No Auth (expects 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/traders

###

