# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# REPORTS (TAX_ADMIN+ required)
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### [REPORTS-01] Summary — Last 7 Days
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/summary?period=7d
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [REPORTS-02] Summary — Last 30 Days
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/summary?period=30d
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [REPORTS-03] Summary — All Time
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/summary?period=all
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [REPORTS-04] Export CSV — All Traders
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/export?format=csv
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [REPORTS-05] Export CSV — Filtered by Channel
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/export?format=csv&channel=web
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [REPORTS-06] Export CSV — No Auth (expects 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/export?format=csv

###

