# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# AUDIT LOGS (SYS_ADMIN only)
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### [AUDIT-01] List Audit Logs — All
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/audit-logs?page=1&page_size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [AUDIT-02] Filter by Action
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/audit-logs?action=CREATE_TRADER&page=1&page_size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [AUDIT-03] Filter by Action: LOGIN_SUCCESS
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/audit-logs?action=LOGIN_SUCCESS&page=1&page_size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [AUDIT-04] Filter by Date Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/audit-logs?date_from=2026-01-01&date_to=2026-03-31&page=1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [AUDIT-05] Audit Logs — TAX_ADMIN Forbidden (expects 403)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/audit-logs
Authorization: Bearer {{taxAdminToken}}

###

### [AUDIT-06] Audit Logs — No Auth (expects 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/audit-logs

